==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slater
<hw>Slat"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who lays slates,
or whose occupation is to slate buildings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slater</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Slater
<hw>Slat"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any terrestrial
isopod crustacean of the genus <gen>Porcellio</gen> and allied genera; a
sow bug.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slating</ent>⟦br⟧
